Taxonomic Notes: —Maya-Lastra & Steinman (2018) consider the combinations proposed by Fernández Casas (2002) to validate those initially made by Pax & Hoffmann (1931) as superfluous, an opinion corroborated here, since although Pax & Hoffmann did not make reference to the basionym, their combinations were published before January 1, 1953 , which according to Article 41.4 of the ICN (
Turland et al. 2018
) is correct.
